Mr. Mime (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0121: Starmie
Pokémon
#0123: Scyther →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Mr. Mime (TCG Pocket).

Mr. Mime has been featured on 28 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Mr. Mime cards are normally Psychic-type or Water-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Mr. Mime

Mr. Mime
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
